      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, you said it might interact with the Zoloft... what kind of interaction do you mean? Like, is it dangerous if I take them at the same time while I'm tapering off, or is it just gonna make the nausea worse? i really want to start the St Johns Wort tomorrow so i can get off the sertraline as fast as possible.",
